  "text": "G.S. Sukhatme is with the Robotic Embedded Systems Laboratory, University of Southern California, Los Angeles, CA 90089, USA gaurav@usc.edu allow measurements of the distance between transponder and receiver or between two modems. One example of a ranging measurement device is provided by [CITATION_1] where the Woods Hole Oceanographic Institute (WHOI) micro-modem is presented.",
